\begin_layout Standard
CTCS uses centred in space and time discretisations for gradients:
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\frac{\partial\phi}{\partial x}_{j}=\phi_{j}^{\prime}\approx\opttext{\frac{\phi_{j+1}-\phi_{j-1}}{2\Delta x}}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


