\end_inset


\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

Rearrange to find 
\begin_inset Formula $f_{j}^{\prime}$
\end_inset

:
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $f_{j}^{\prime}=\left(-f_{j+2}+4f_{j+1}-3f_{j}\right)/(2\Delta x)+O(\Delta x^{2})$
\end_inset


\end_layout

