\end_inset


\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

Eliminate the largest unknown, 
\begin_inset Formula $f_{j}^{\prime}$
\end_inset

 by calculating 
\begin_inset Formula $f_{j+2}-2f_{j+1}$
