\begin_inset Formula $\implies\Delta x_{1}^{2}f_{c}-\Delta x_{2}^{2}f_{a}=\left(\Delta x_{1}^{2}-\Delta x_{2}^{2}\right)f_{b}+\Delta x_{1}\Delta x_{2}\left(\Delta x_{1}+\Delta x_{2}\right)f_{b}^{\prime}+O(\Delta x^{5})$
