\begin_inset Formula $\implies f_{b}^{\prime}=\frac{\Delta x_{1}^{2}f_{c}-\Delta x_{2}^{2}f_{a}-\left(\Delta x_{1}^{2}-\Delta x_{2}^{2}\right)f_{b}}{\Delta x_{1}\Delta x_{2}\left(\Delta x_{1}+\Delta x_{2}\right)}+O(\Delta x^{2})$
