status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

}
\backslash
step{
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
If 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

 is a real number, then the numerical method is stable 
\begin_inset Formula $\iff|A|\le1$
\end_inset


\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
step{
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
If 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

 is a complex number then the numerical method is stable 
\begin_inset Formula $\iff||A||\le1$
\end_inset


\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

}
\backslash
step{
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
If 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

 is a matrix then the numerical method is stable if 
\begin_inset Formula $\rho(A)\le1$
