\begin_layout Standard
The initial conditions of any PDE, or the solution at any time, can be written
 as a sum of Fourier modes:
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\phi(x,t)=\sum_{k}A_{k}(t)\ e^{ikx}
\end{equation}

